Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.60,0:02:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,000)}第7話 小櫻首次挑戰當怪盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.65,0:02:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快好了，再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.35,0:02:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊，這是我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，畫得很可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉才沒長得這麼奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.65,0:02:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?我覺得畫得很像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳再看清楚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.35,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?眼睛很亮又是雙眼皮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳還要再長一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我把話說完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在樓上做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在畫圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們工藝課要去美術館寫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在練習啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.65,0:03:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習畫圖怎麼會那麼吵呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不一邊說話的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法畫得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳去美術館也那麼吵的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被趕出去的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.65,0:03:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過別吵到來看畫的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的會被趕出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是不會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本美術館的館長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天讓各位畫的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.85,0:04:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大廳以及中庭的雕像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，這裡真安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，真的很安靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在中庭畫圖的人請跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，妳要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想在這裡畫那個雕像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得不錯的話一起畫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千春她們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也想去中庭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，開始畫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了，知世妳呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，我們去中庭看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先把這張畫完成再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼去中庭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我，放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要破壞畫作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有破壞畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我爸爸的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸原本是想畫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是誰亂改畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成那個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.85,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安份一點，跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.85,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"微笑"，橘天海?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集合時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美術館的畫會動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就突然聽不見聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是一瞬間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是那個吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.35,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不幸過世失志的畫家心有怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幅畫一定是被咀咒才會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼可怕嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我倒不覺得可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.65,0:07:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳對鬼跟幽靈很敏感對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.15,0:07:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說會不會又是那個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，庫洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起去查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.75,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了妳還要出去啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.35,0:07:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我想來看看月亮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多星星喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃矢在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，他在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，別告訴我哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻在二樓睡覺對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我沒見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳不能太晚回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子沮喪一下子高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會不會覺得我太沒家教了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他很關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，但是但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點，知世在等我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"默牌(silent)"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是沈默的意思吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種牌最討厭吵鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.05,0:09:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以它才會躲在安靜的美術館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"默牌"有什麼魔力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.45,0:09:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天它只是讓聲音消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙能讓聲音消失的同時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣也算封印獸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙幾乎不說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太了解它的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，換衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的衣服比較樸素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.75,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，因為怪盜不能太顯眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是要當小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要潛入警備森嚴的美術館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是要好好偽裝才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.05,0:10:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美術館警衛的輪班表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害，怎麼拿到的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我後來又去美術館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們借的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照這張表看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們再去巡邏那張畫的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好是1小時之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把鈴聲設定在5分鐘前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始出動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是來偷美術品的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小偷囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?我們不能不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕走他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有什麼主意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.35,0:11:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你躲在那裡對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真大膽，根本不逃耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法，那就繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.45,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裡的守護神，快給我離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼守護神嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你在畫作上惡作劇的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出乎我們的意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個男孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認識他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天在這裡看過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快救救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是普通的玩偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.45,0:12:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是腹語罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.15,0:13:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你是小偷，請原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長得真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.75,0:13:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我被它嚇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們若是在畫上惡作劇的犯人，我可不饒你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是美麗的怪盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會做那種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪盜?這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.45,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，我們只是忘了東西回來拿而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼穿成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.65,0:13:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是對畫惡作劇都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，小勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我的名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.75,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?原來是那時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小勇，你真的想割破那幅畫嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想割破它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想要把它恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幅畫是我爸爸畫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.45,0:14:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸是那位叫橘天海的畫家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過天海畫家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他畫了很多了不起的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.75,0:14:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他去年好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年秋天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他生病過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幅畫是去年夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟爸爸最後一次家族旅行時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸為了留下那次去海邊的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.45,0:14:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全神灌注畫出的我的畫像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也說那是她最喜歡的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道誰在上面亂畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我跟爸爸最珍貴的回憶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過份了，我了解你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的畫被亂畫時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也非常生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小勇，我們來幫你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?人家好意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.95,0:15:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的腹語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說，我們一起查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過別妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不討人喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們浪費太多時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能在小勇面前用魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇他也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我引開他的注意時妳再動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這幅畫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是"默牌"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫上的惡作劇還很新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.95,0:15:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是油畫應該很容易弄掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想成為像爸爸一樣的畫家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定會成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，小勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要修復油畫很困難耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是交給美術館的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不交給那些人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.25,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能，我自己就能修改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說話太大聲，警衛會聽見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中庭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要接近爸爸的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會被推到外面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是"默牌"的魔力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要出聲就會被趕出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好不是在白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們相信嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為是鬼怪，白天來也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，小勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你白天跟現在都太大聲才會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.95,0:17:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要安靜一點，鬼怪大概也就不會作怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說，只要不出聲就行了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是鬼怪的作怪就弄不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要回去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，從這裡可以進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.15,0:17:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳用魔法把它當作是鬼怪作怪\N大概就可以瞞過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.95,0:17:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連這點聲音都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(安靜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(沒時間了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾，哈啾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是打噴嚏也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連咒語都不能唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，小勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警衛就快要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我們被抓了 怎麼收拾"默牌"呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃，別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被抓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.65,0:19:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先躲一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救他才行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!放開我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是白天那個男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封印玻璃映出我們的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「影」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!讓我下去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安份一點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!別跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復你原來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.75,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復你原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常成功喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底躲在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.05,0:20:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了!畫變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.35,0:20:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行，被警衛抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.75,0:20:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢?你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，恢復原形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.95,0:21:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳是女孩啊，對不起，我搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才該道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.55,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳留長髮好可愛，對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，謝謝妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.55,0:21:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為了爸爸拼了命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.75,0:21:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來她不是小勇而是小優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼孝順父母的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是感人的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可真帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成，作戰結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.95,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳怎麼會想到用影牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.95,0:22:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想到小可的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是我的功勞囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.35,0:22:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有庫洛牌在附近…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.18,0:23:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}包在小可身上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.63,0:23:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有每週準時收看呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.83,0:23:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.83,0:23:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介紹最多小櫻情報的"包在小可身上"又到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.13,0:23:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，立刻開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.93,0:23:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次也是介紹戰服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.73,0:23:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次跟以往的戰服不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.43,0:23:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,款式很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.93,0:23:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小短褲也很帥氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.33,0:24:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世說怪盜的服裝不能太顯眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.23,0:24:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這套服裝不太顯眼卻很怪異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.83,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是"小可觀察時間"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世的多功能錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉紅色很可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.43,0:24:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有鈴聲、馬錶各式各樣的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.93,0:24:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一集就要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.33,0:24:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻的服裝越來越有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.33,0:24:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也要注意以後出現的服裝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.53,0:24:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.23,0:24:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們班有個來自香港的轉學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.53,0:24:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他卻瞪著我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.53,0:24:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.23,0:24:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他好像知道我在回收庫洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.73,0:24:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬要我把回收的牌給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.11,0:24:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛魔法使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.72,0:24:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「小櫻的對手登場」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.55,0:24:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也與小櫻一起解除封印!
